🧠 AI-Powered Study Buddy
An AI-driven study companion that explains complex topics in simple terms, summarizes notes (including uploaded PDF/DOCX/PPTX/TXT files), generates quizzes, and creates flashcards — all powered by Groq's LLaMA 3.3 70B model.

---
✨ Features
💡 Topic Explainer — explanations at simple, medium, or advanced level
📄 Notes Summarizer — paste text or upload PDF / DOCX / PPTX / TXT files
🏆 Quiz Generator — auto-generated MCQs with instant scoring and explanations
🗂️ Flashcard Generator — flip-card style study cards
🕘 Study History — tracks and stores all past sessions per user
🔐 Authentication — JWT-based login & register
🌓 Dark / Light Mode
---
🛠️ Tech Stack
Layer	Technology
Frontend	React (Vite) + Tailwind CSS
Backend	FastAPI (Python)
Database	MongoDB Atlas
AI	Groq API (LLaMA 3.3 70B)
Auth	JWT + Bcrypt
File Parsing	PyMuPDF, python-docx, python-pptx
---
